---
// Peluquería VIP Granada — página autónoma con su propio sistema de diseño (tema dorado)
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Barbería VIP Granada | Cortes para Caballeros</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Barbería VIP Granada — Cortes de cabello, arreglo de barba y cejas para caballeros. Reserva tu cita online en C. Pintor Zuloaga, 22, Granada.">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 32 32'%3E%3Crect width='32' height='32' rx='7' fill='%230d0d0f'/%3E%3Ctext x='3' y='23' font-family='monospace' font-weight='bold' font-size='19' fill='%23c9a84c'%3EDM%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --gold: #c9a84c;
            --gold-light: #e8c96e;
            --gold-dim: rgba(201,168,76,0.14);
            --dark: #0d0d0f;
            --dark-2: #131315;
            --dark-3: #1c1c1f;
            --dark-4: #232326;
            --text: #f4efe6;
            --text-muted: #948e82;
            --border: rgba(201,168,76,0.16);
            --red: #ef4444;
            --tr: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94);
        }
        *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
        html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
        body{background:var(--dark);color:var(--text);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden}
        ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px}
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--dark)}
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--gold);border-radius:2px}
        img{display:block;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}

        /* BACK */
        .back-link{
            position:fixed;top:20px;left:24px;z-index:1100;
            display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
            color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:500;
            padding:7px 14px;background:rgba(13,13,15,0.9);border:1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius:50px;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);transition:var(--tr);letter-spacing:.5px;
        }
        .back-link:hover{color:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold)}

        /* HEADER */
        .header{
            position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:900;
            padding:0 60px;height:76px;
            display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
            background:rgba(13,13,15,0.93);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
            border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:var(--tr);
        }
        .logo-bar{display:flex;flex-direction:column;line-height:1.15}
        .logo-name{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.35rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase}
        .logo-sub{font-size:0.58rem;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--text-muted);text-transform:uppercase}
        .nav-ul{display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none}
        .nav-ul a{color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.83rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color .3s;position:relative}
        .nav-ul a::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-4px;left:0;width:0;height:1px;background:var(--gold);transition:width .3s}
        .nav-ul a:hover{color:var(--gold)}
        .nav-ul a:hover::after{width:100%}
        .nav-cta{background:var(--gold)!important;color:var(--dark)!important;padding:9px 20px!important;border-radius:4px!important;font-weight:600!important}
        .nav-cta:hover{background:var(--gold-light)!important;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(201,168,76,.35)!important}
        .nav-cta::after{display:none!important}

        /* HERO */
        .hero{
            min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
            position:relative;overflow:hidden;text-align:center;padding:100px 40px 80px;
        }
        .hero-bg{
            position:absolute;inset:0;
            background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 55% at 50% -5%,rgba(201,168,76,.07) 0%,transparent 70%),var(--dark);
        }
        .hero-grid-lines{
            position:absolute;inset:0;
            background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(201,168,76,.025) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(201,168,76,.025) 1px,transparent 1px);
            background-size:50px 50px;
        }
        .hero-content{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:720px}
        .hero-badge{
            display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
            font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;
            color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:28px;padding:7px 18px;
            border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:50px;
        }
        .hero-badge::before,.hero-badge::after{content:'◆';font-size:.45rem}
        .hero h1{
            font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
            font-size:clamp(2.8rem,8vw,5.5rem);font-weight:900;line-height:1.05;margin-bottom:8px;
        }
        .line-gold{
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-light),var(--gold));
            -webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;
            background-size:200%;animation:gradShift 4s ease infinite;
        }
        @keyframes gradShift{0%,100%{background-position:0% 50%}50%{background-position:100% 50%}}
        .hero-divider{width:50px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold),transparent);margin:26px auto}
        .hero p{font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-muted);max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 42px;line-height:1.8}
        .hero-btns{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
        .hero-scroll{
            position:absolute;bottom:36px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
            display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:6px;
            color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.68rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;
            animation:scrollBob 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes scrollBob{0%,100%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(7px)}}

        /* BUTTONS */
        .btn-gold{
            display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:15px 34px;
            background:var(--gold);color:var(--dark);text-decoration:none;
            font-weight:700;font-size:.88rem;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;
            border-radius:4px;border:2px solid var(--gold);cursor:pointer;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;transition:var(--tr);
        }
        .btn-gold:hover{background:var(--gold-light);transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 14px 36px rgba(201,168,76,.35)}
        .btn-ghost{
            display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:15px 34px;
            background:transparent;color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none;
            font-weight:600;font-size:.88rem;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;
            border-radius:4px;border:2px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;transition:var(--tr);
        }
        .btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold-dim);transform:translateY(-3px)}

        /* SECTIONS */
        .section-full{padding:100px 0;background:var(--dark-2)}
        .section-std{padding:100px 60px;max-width:1300px;margin:0 auto}
        .inner{max-width:1300px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 60px}
        .slabel{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
        .slabel::before{content:'';width:28px;height:1px;background:var(--gold)}
        .stitle{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:16px}
        .ssub{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.93rem;max-width:480px;line-height:1.8}

        /* SERVICES */
        .services-grid{
            display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
            gap:1px;background:var(--border);
            border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:56px;
        }
        .svc{
            background:var(--dark-2);padding:42px 36px;transition:var(--tr);position:relative;cursor:default;
        }
        .svc:hover{background:var(--dark-3)}
        .svc::before{
            content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;
            background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold),transparent);
            opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s;
        }
        .svc:hover::before{opacity:1}
        .svc-icon{
            width:50px;height:50px;background:var(--gold-dim);border:1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
            font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:20px;transition:var(--tr);
        }
        .svc:hover .svc-icon{background:rgba(201,168,76,.25);transform:scale(1.1)}
        .svc-name{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}
        .svc-desc{font-size:.84rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:22px}
        .svc-price{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold)}
        .svc-price small{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-muted);font-weight:400}

        /* BOOKING */
        .booking-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.4fr;gap:70px;align-items:start;margin-top:56px}
        .booking-side p{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:32px}
        .bsteps{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px}
        .bstep{display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start}
        .bdot{
            width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid var(--border);
            background:var(--dark-3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
            font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0;transition:var(--tr);
        }
        .bdot.done{background:var(--gold);color:var(--dark);border-color:var(--gold)}
        .bstep-info h5{font-size:.83rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px}
        .bstep-info p{font-size:.76rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0}

        /* Active booking banner */
        .active-booking-banner{
            background:rgba(201,168,76,.07);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.3);
            border-radius:12px;padding:18px 22px;margin-bottom:14px;
            display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:14px;
        }
        .abn-info{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px}
        .abn-icon{font-size:1.4rem}
        .abn-text strong{display:block;color:var(--gold);font-size:.85rem;margin-bottom:3px}
        .abn-text p{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0}
        .btn-cancel-booking{
            background:rgba(239,68,68,.1);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.3);
            color:var(--red);padding:7px 14px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;
            font-size:.78rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;transition:var(--tr);white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;
        }
        .btn-cancel-booking:hover{background:rgba(239,68,68,.2)}

        /* Form card */
        .form-card{background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden}
        .fstep{display:none;padding:36px;animation:stepIn .35s ease-out}
        .fstep.active{display:block}
        @keyframes stepIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(16px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}}
        .fstep-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:26px;padding-bottom:18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
        .fstep-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.2rem}
        .fstep-step{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:1px}

        /* Service selection */
        .svc-pick-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:9px;margin-bottom:26px}
        .svc-pick-btn{
            padding:16px 20px;background:var(--dark-4);border:1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius:10px;color:var(--text-muted);cursor:pointer;text-align:left;
            transition:var(--tr);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
            display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
        }
        .svc-pick-btn:hover{border-color:rgba(201,168,76,.4);background:var(--dark-3);color:var(--text)}
        .svc-pick-btn.selected{border-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold-dim);color:var(--gold)}
        .spb-name{font-weight:600;font-size:.88rem}
        .spb-right{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:2px;flex-shrink:0}
        .spb-price{font-size:.92rem;font-weight:700;font-family:'Playfair Display',serif}
        .spb-dur{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-muted)}
        .svc-pick-btn.selected .spb-dur{color:rgba(201,168,76,.7)}

        /* Calendar */
        .cal-month{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:12px}
        .cal-month-name{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--gold)}
        .cal-nav{background:none;border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-muted);
            width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;font-size:.8rem;transition:var(--tr)}
        .cal-nav:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold)}
        .cal-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:4px;margin-bottom:20px}
        .cal-day-lbl{text-align:center;font-size:.65rem;color:var(--text-muted);padding:5px 0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}
        .cal-day{
            aspect-ratio:1;background:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;
            border-radius:7px;color:var(--text-muted);cursor:pointer;font-size:.82rem;
            font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;transition:var(--tr);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
        }
        .cal-day:hover:not(:disabled){border-color:rgba(201,168,76,.35);color:var(--text)}
        .cal-day.selected{background:var(--gold);color:var(--dark);border-color:var(--gold);font-weight:700}
        .cal-day:disabled{opacity:.2;cursor:not-allowed}
        .cal-day.empty{cursor:default;pointer-events:none}

        /* Time slots */
        .time-label{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:10px}
        .time-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:7px;margin-bottom:24px}
        .time-btn{
            padding:9px 6px;background:var(--dark-4);border:1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius:7px;color:var(--text-muted);cursor:pointer;font-size:.8rem;
            font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;transition:var(--tr);text-align:center;
        }
        .time-btn:hover:not(.taken){border-color:rgba(201,168,76,.4);color:var(--text)}
        .time-btn.selected{background:var(--gold);color:var(--dark);border-color:var(--gold);font-weight:600}
        .time-btn.taken{opacity:.35;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:line-through;position:relative}
        .time-btn.taken:hover{border-color:rgba(239,68,68,.4);color:#ef4444;opacity:.6}

        /* Toast notification */
        .barber-toast{
            position:fixed;bottom:32px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(16px);
            background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.35);
            color:var(--text);padding:14px 24px 14px 18px;border-radius:50px;
            font-size:.84rem;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;z-index:9999;
            opacity:0;transition:all .35s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);
            white-space:nowrap;box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
            display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;pointer-events:none;
        }
        .barber-toast.show{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}
        .barber-toast i{color:#ef4444}

        /* Summary & fields */
        .summary-box{
            background:var(--dark-4);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;
            padding:22px;margin-bottom:22px;
        }
        .summary-box h5{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:14px;letter-spacing:1px}
        .sum-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.07);font-size:.83rem}
        .sum-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
        .sum-lbl{color:var(--text-muted)}
        .sum-val{color:var(--text);font-weight:500}
        .sum-val.gold{color:var(--gold);font-weight:700}
        .frow{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px}
        .fgroup{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;margin-bottom:12px}
        .fgroup label{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)}
        .fgroup input{
            background:var(--dark-4);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;
            padding:12px 15px;color:var(--text);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:.88rem;
            outline:none;transition:var(--tr);width:100%;cursor:text;
        }
        .fgroup input:focus{border-color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,168,76,.03)}
        .fgroup input::placeholder{color:var(--text-muted);opacity:.45}
        .fnav{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end}
        .btn-next{
            padding:13px 24px;border-radius:7px;font-size:.83rem;font-weight:600;
            cursor:pointer;transition:var(--tr);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;border:none;
            background:var(--gold);color:var(--dark);
        }
        .btn-next:hover{background:var(--gold-light);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 7px 20px rgba(201,168,76,.3)}
        .btn-next:disabled{opacity:.35;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none;box-shadow:none}
        .btn-back{
            padding:13px 24px;border-radius:7px;font-size:.83rem;font-weight:600;
            cursor:pointer;transition:var(--tr);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
            background:transparent;color:var(--text-muted);border:1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .btn-back:hover{color:var(--text);border-color:rgba(201,168,76,.3)}

        /* Confirmation */
        .confirm-screen{text-align:center;padding:46px 36px}
        .confirm-icon{
            width:76px;height:76px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(201,168,76,.18),rgba(201,168,76,.05));
            border:2px solid var(--gold);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
            font-size:1.9rem;color:var(--gold);margin:0 auto 24px;
            animation:popIn .5s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1);
        }
        @keyframes popIn{from{transform:scale(0);opacity:0}to{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}}
        .confirm-screen h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.7rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:10px}
        .confirm-screen p{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:28px}

        /* GALLERY */
        .gallery-grid{
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows:260px 260px;
            gap:10px;margin-top:56px;
        }
        .g-item{border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;cursor:pointer;background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid var(--border)}
        .g-item:first-child{grid-row:span 2}
        .g-item img{transition:transform .5s ease}
        .g-item:hover img{transform:scale(1.05)}
        .g-overlay{
            position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(13,13,15,.7),transparent);
            opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:16px;
        }
        .g-item:hover .g-overlay{opacity:1}
        .g-caption{font-size:.75rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)}
        .g-placeholder{
            width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
            gap:10px;font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--gold);opacity:.3;
        }
        .g-placeholder span{font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted)}

        /* MAP */
        .map-section{padding:0 60px 100px;max-width:1300px;margin:0 auto}
        .map-wrapper{
            border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--border);
            height:400px;margin-top:36px;position:relative;
        }
        .map-wrapper iframe{width:100%;height:100%;border:0;filter:invert(90%) hue-rotate(180deg)}

        /* ABOUT */
        .about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:70px;align-items:start;margin-top:56px}
        .about-visual{
            background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;
            padding:40px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
        }
        .about-visual::before{
            content:'';position:absolute;top:-40%;right:-30%;width:260px;height:260px;
            background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(201,168,76,.05) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;
        }
        .vip-mono{
            font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:6.5rem;font-weight:900;
            color:var(--gold);opacity:.1;line-height:1;margin-bottom:16px;letter-spacing:-3px;
        }
        .stats-strip{
            display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;
            background:var(--border);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;
        }
        .stat-c{background:var(--dark-3);padding:18px 12px;text-align:center}
        .stat-num{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px}
        .stat-lbl{font-size:.65rem;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}
        .hours-table{margin-top:22px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
        .hour-row{
            display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:9px 14px;
            background:var(--dark-4);border-radius:6px;font-size:.8rem;
        }
        .hour-row .day{color:var(--text-muted)}
        .hour-row .time{color:var(--gold);font-weight:600}
        .hour-row.closed .time{color:#444}
        .about-text p{color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:18px;font-size:.92rem}
        .features-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-top:22px}
        .features-list li{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:.87rem;color:var(--text-muted)}
        .features-list li::before{content:'◆';color:var(--gold);font-size:.45rem;flex-shrink:0}

        /* CONTACT CARDS */
        .contact-cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:56px}
        .cc{
            background:var(--dark-3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;
            padding:30px 22px;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;
            transition:var(--tr);display:block;
        }
        .cc:hover{border-color:rgba(201,168,76,.35);transform:translateY(-6px);box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(201,168,76,.07)}
        .cc-icon{
            width:52px;height:52px;background:var(--gold-dim);border:1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
            font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--gold);margin:0 auto 16px;transition:var(--tr);
        }
        .cc:hover .cc-icon{background:rgba(201,168,76,.24);transform:scale(1.1)}
        .cc h4{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:7px}
        .cc p{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.5}

        /* ACCESSIBILITY WIDGET */
        html{font-size:var(--a11y-base,16px)}
        body.a11y-high-contrast::after,body.a11y-inverted::after,body.a11y-grayscale::after,body.a11y-deuteranopia::after,body.a11y-protanopia::after{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:99998}
        body.a11y-high-contrast::after{backdrop-filter:contrast(1.5) brightness(1.1);-webkit-backdrop-filter:contrast(1.5) brightness(1.1)}
        body.a11y-inverted::after{backdrop-filter:invert(100%) hue-rotate(180deg);-webkit-backdrop-filter:invert(100%) hue-rotate(180deg)}
        body.a11y-grayscale::after{backdrop-filter:grayscale(100%);-webkit-backdrop-filter:grayscale(100%)}
        body.a11y-deuteranopia::after{backdrop-filter:saturate(0.6) hue-rotate(-15deg) sepia(0.2);-webkit-backdrop-filter:saturate(0.6) hue-rotate(-15deg) sepia(0.2)}
        body.a11y-protanopia::after{backdrop-filter:saturate(0.5) hue-rotate(-30deg) sepia(0.25);-webkit-backdrop-filter:saturate(0.5) hue-rotate(-30deg) sepia(0.25)}
        body.a11y-reduced-motion *{animation-duration:.05s!important;transition-duration:.05s!important}
        body.a11y-no-motion *{animation:none!important;transition:none!important}

        .a11y-widget{position:fixed;bottom:28px;left:24px;z-index:99999;font-size:14px}
        .a11y-fab{
            display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
            padding:10px 16px;background:rgba(13,13,15,.95);
            border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.4);border-radius:50px;
            color:var(--gold);font-size:12px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
            cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s ease;
            backdrop-filter:blur(12px);box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
            font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.5px;
        }
        .a11y-fab:hover{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:0 6px 28px rgba(201,168,76,.3);transform:translateY(-2px)}
        .a11y-fab i{font-size:14px}
        .a11y-panel{
            position:absolute;bottom:48px;left:0;width:296px;
            background:rgba(13,13,15,.99);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.22);
            border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;display:none;
            backdrop-filter:blur(20px);box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.8);
            font-size:13px;
        }
        .a11y-panel.open{display:block;animation:panelUp .22s ease-out}
        @keyframes panelUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
        .a11y-ph{
            display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
            padding:13px 16px 11px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.12);
            font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);
        }
        .a11y-xbtn{background:none;border:none;color:var(--text-muted);cursor:pointer;font-size:15px;padding:3px 6px;border-radius:4px;line-height:1}
        .a11y-xbtn:hover{color:var(--text)}
        .a11y-row-item{
            display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
            padding:10px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.06);gap:8px;
        }
        .a11y-row-item:last-of-type{border-bottom:none}
        .a11y-row-lbl{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);flex-shrink:0}
        .a11y-chips{display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:nowrap;overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none}
        .a11y-chips::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
        .a11y-chip{
            padding:4px 9px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
            border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.14);border-radius:5px;
            color:var(--text-muted);font-size:11px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
            cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1.3;
        }
        .a11y-chip:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold)}
        .a11y-chip.on{background:rgba(201,168,76,.14);border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold);font-weight:700}
        .a11y-rbtn{
            display:block;width:calc(100% - 32px);margin:8px 16px 12px;padding:8px;
            background:transparent;border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.15);border-radius:7px;
            color:var(--text-muted);font-size:11px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;cursor:pointer;
            text-align:center;transition:all .18s;letter-spacing:.5px;
        }
        .a11y-rbtn:hover{border-color:rgba(239,68,68,.4);color:#ef4444}

        /* HAMBURGER MÓVIL */
        .nav-hamburger-pel{
            display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;
            background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;padding:8px;border-radius:6px;
            transition:background .2s;
        }
        .nav-hamburger-pel:hover{background:rgba(201,168,76,.1)}
        .ham-line-pel{display:block;width:22px;height:2px;background:var(--gold);border-radius:2px;transition:all .25s cubic-bezier(.25,.46,.45,.94)}
        .nav-hamburger-pel.open .ham-line-pel:nth-child(1){transform:translateY(7px) rotate(45deg)}
        .nav-hamburger-pel.open .ham-line-pel:nth-child(2){opacity:0;transform:scaleX(0)}
        .nav-hamburger-pel.open .ham-line-pel:nth-child(3){transform:translateY(-7px) rotate(-45deg)}

        /* FOOTER */
        footer{
            border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:36px 60px;
            display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
        }
        .f-logo{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase}
        .f-copy{font-size:.76rem;color:var(--text-muted)}
        .f-copy a{color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none}
        .f-links{display:flex;gap:22px}
        .f-links a{color:var(--text-muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:.78rem;transition:color .3s}
        .f-links a:hover{color:var(--gold)}

        /* RESPONSIVE */
        @media(max-width:1024px){
            .header,.section-std,.map-section{padding-left:40px;padding-right:40px}
            .inner{padding:0 40px}
            .services-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
            .booking-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:36px}
            .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}
            .contact-cards{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
            footer{padding:28px 40px}
        }
        @media(max-width:768px){
            .header{padding:0 20px;position:relative}
            .inner{padding:0 20px}
            .section-std{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px}
            .map-section{padding:0 20px 70px}
            .nav-ul{
                display:none;
                position:absolute;top:100%;left:0;right:0;
                flex-direction:column;gap:0;
                background:rgba(13,13,15,.98);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
                border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);z-index:1000;padding:6px 0;
            }
            .nav-ul.open{display:flex}
            .nav-ul li a{display:block;padding:13px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:.85rem}
            .nav-ul li:last-child a{border-bottom:none}
            .nav-hamburger-pel{display:flex}
            .services-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
            .gallery-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;grid-template-rows:auto}
            .g-item:first-child{grid-row:span 1}
            .contact-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
            .frow{grid-template-columns:1fr}
            .time-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
            footer{flex-direction:column;gap:16px;text-align:center;padding:24px 20px}
            .back-link{top:12px;left:12px;font-size:.72rem;padding:6px 11px}
            .svc-pick-grid{gap:7px}
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<a href="/" class="back-link"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Portfolio</a>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="header" id="hdr">
    <div class="logo-bar">
        <span class="logo-name">Barbería VIP</span>
        <span class="logo-sub">Granada · C. Pintor Zuloaga</span>
    </div>
    <nav style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px">
        <ul class="nav-ul" id="nav-ul-pel">
            <li><a href="#servicios">Servicios</a></li>
            <li><a href="#reservar">Reservar</a></li>
            <li><a href="#galeria">Galería</a></li>
            <li><a href="#nosotros">Nosotros</a></li>
            <li><a href="#reservar" class="nav-cta">Reservar cita</a></li>
        </ul>
        <button class="nav-hamburger-pel" id="nav-ham-pel" aria-label="Abrir menú" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="ham-line-pel"></span>
            <span class="ham-line-pel"></span>
            <span class="ham-line-pel"></span>
        </button>
    </nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="inicio">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-grid-lines"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-badge">Barbería · Granada · Desde 2018</div>
        <h1>Tu mejor<br><span class="line-gold">versión</span></h1>
        <div class="hero-divider"></div>
        <p>Cortes para caballeros que saben lo que quieren. Precisión, estilo y ambiente exclusivo en el corazón de Granada.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
            <a href="#reservar" class="btn-gold"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i> Reservar Cita</a>
            <a href="#servicios" class="btn-ghost">Ver Servicios</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i><span>Descubrir</span></div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICIOS -->
<div class="section-full" id="servicios">
    <div class="inner">
        <div class="slabel">Lo que ofrecemos</div>
        <h2 class="stitle">Servicios</h2>
        <p class="ssub">Tres opciones claras. Sin complicaciones. El resultado que buscas.</p>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="svc">
                <div class="svc-icon"><i class="fas fa-cut"></i></div>
                <div class="svc-name">Corte de Pelo</div>
                <div class="svc-desc">Corte clásico o degradado a tu gusto. Tijera o máquina, con el acabado perfecto para tu tipo de cabello y estilo.</div>
                <div class="svc-price">11€ <small>/ 30 min</small></div>
            </div>
            <div class="svc">
                <div class="svc-icon"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i></div>
                <div class="svc-name">Corte + Barba</div>
                <div class="svc-desc">Corte completo más arreglo o perfilado de barba. El pack más solicitado para un look impecable de arriba a abajo.</div>
                <div class="svc-price">16€ <small>/ 45 min</small></div>
            </div>
            <div class="svc">
                <div class="svc-icon"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
                <div class="svc-name">Corte + Barba + Cejas</div>
                <div class="svc-desc">El servicio completo. Corte, arreglo de barba y definición de cejas. El look más cuidado para quien no deja nada al azar.</div>
                <div class="svc-price">20€ <small>/ 55 min</small></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- RESERVAR CITA -->
<section class="section-std" id="reservar">
    <div class="slabel">Online · 24/7</div>
    <h2 class="stitle">Reservar Cita</h2>
    <p class="ssub">Elige tu servicio, fecha y hora. Si ya tienes una cita, podrás cancelarla antes de reservar una nueva.</p>

    <div class="booking-layout">
        <div class="booking-side">
            <p>Sin esperas, sin llamadas. Reserva en 2 minutos y recibe confirmación inmediata.</p>
            <div class="bsteps">
                <div class="bstep"><div class="bdot done" id="d1">1</div><div class="bstep-info"><h5>Servicio</h5><p>Elige qué quieres hacerte</p></div></div>
                <div class="bstep"><div class="bdot" id="d2">2</div><div class="bstep-info"><h5>Fecha y Hora</h5><p>Cuándo quieres venir</p></div></div>
                <div class="bstep"><div class="bdot" id="d3">3</div><div class="bstep-info"><h5>Tus Datos</h5><p>Nombre y teléfono</p></div></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div>
            <!-- Banner de reserva activa (se inyecta con JS) -->
            <div id="active-banner"></div>

            <div class="form-card">
                <!-- PASO 1: Servicio -->
                <div class="fstep active" id="s1">
                    <div class="fstep-header">
                        <span class="fstep-title">¿Qué servicio?</span>
                        <span class="fstep-step">Paso 1 / 3</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="svc-pick-grid">
                        <button class="svc-pick-btn" data-svc="Corte de Pelo" data-price="11€" data-dur="30 min">
                            <span class="spb-name">Corte de Pelo</span>
                            <span class="spb-right"><span class="spb-price">11€</span><span class="spb-dur">30 min</span></span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="svc-pick-btn" data-svc="Corte + Barba" data-price="16€" data-dur="45 min">
                            <span class="spb-name">Corte + Barba</span>
                            <span class="spb-right"><span class="spb-price">16€</span><span class="spb-dur">45 min</span></span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="svc-pick-btn" data-svc="Corte + Barba + Cejas" data-price="20€" data-dur="55 min">
                            <span class="spb-name">Corte + Barba + Cejas</span>
                            <span class="spb-right"><span class="spb-price">20€</span><span class="spb-dur">55 min</span></span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fnav">
                        <button class="btn-next" id="to2" disabled>Continuar <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- PASO 2: Fecha & Hora -->
                <div class="fstep" id="s2">
                    <div class="fstep-header">
                        <span class="fstep-title">Elige fecha y hora</span>
                        <span class="fstep-step">Paso 2 / 3</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cal-month">
                        <button class="cal-nav" id="cal-prev"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></button>
                        <span class="cal-month-name" id="cal-title"></span>
                        <button class="cal-nav" id="cal-next"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cal-grid" id="cal-grid"></div>
                    <div class="time-label">Hora disponible</div>
                    <div class="time-grid" id="time-grid"></div>
                    <div class="fnav">
                        <button class="btn-back" id="back1">Atrás</button>
                        <button class="btn-next" id="to3" disabled>Continuar <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- PASO 3: Datos -->
                <div class="fstep" id="s3">
                    <div class="fstep-header">
                        <span class="fstep-title">Tus datos</span>
                        <span class="fstep-step">Paso 3 / 3</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="summary-box">
                        <h5>◆ Resumen</h5>
                        <div class="sum-row"><span class="sum-lbl">Servicio</span><span class="sum-val" id="sv-svc">—</span></div>
                        <div class="sum-row"><span class="sum-lbl">Fecha</span><span class="sum-val" id="sv-date">—</span></div>
                        <div class="sum-row"><span class="sum-lbl">Hora</span><span class="sum-val" id="sv-time">—</span></div>
                        <div class="sum-row"><span class="sum-lbl">Precio</span><span class="sum-val gold" id="sv-price">—</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="frow">
                        <div class="fgroup"><label>Nombre</label><input type="text" id="f-name" placeholder="Tu nombre" autocomplete="given-name"></div>
                        <div class="fgroup"><label>Apellido</label><input type="text" id="f-surname" placeholder="Apellido" autocomplete="family-name"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fgroup"><label>Teléfono</label><input type="tel" id="f-phone" placeholder="6XX XXX XXX" autocomplete="tel"></div>
                    <div class="fgroup"><label>Notas (opcional)</label><input type="text" id="f-notes" placeholder="Estilo, preferencias..."></div>
                    <div class="fnav">
                        <button class="btn-back" id="back2">Atrás</button>
                        <button class="btn-next" id="confirm"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Confirmar</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- CONFIRMACIÓN -->
                <div class="fstep" id="s-ok">
                    <div class="confirm-screen">
                        <div class="confirm-icon"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></div>
                        <h3>¡Reserva Confirmada!</h3>
                        <p id="confirm-msg">Tu cita está registrada.</p>
                        <button class="btn-gold" id="new-booking" style="margin:0 auto;display:inline-flex;"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Nueva Reserva</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- GALERÍA -->
<div class="section-full" id="galeria">
    <div class="inner">
        <div class="slabel">Nuestro Trabajo</div>
        <h2 class="stitle">Galería</h2>
        <p class="ssub">Resultados reales en clientes reales. El trabajo habla solo.</p>
        <div class="gallery-grid">
            <div class="g-item">
                <img src="/peluqueria-fuera.jpg" alt="Fachada Barbería VIP Granada"
                     onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'">
                <div class="g-placeholder" style="display:none"><i class="fas fa-store"></i><span>Nuestra Barbería</span></div>
                <div class="g-overlay"><span class="g-caption">La Barbería</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="g-item">
                <img src="/peluqueria-fuera2.jpg" alt="Entrada Barbería VIP Granada"
                     onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'">
                <div class="g-placeholder" style="display:none"><i class="fas fa-door-open"></i><span>Entrada</span></div>
                <div class="g-overlay"><span class="g-caption">La Entrada</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="g-item">
                <img src="/materiales.jpg" alt="Herramientas y materiales Barbería VIP"
                     onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'">
                <div class="g-placeholder" style="display:none"><i class="fas fa-tools"></i><span>El Material</span></div>
                <div class="g-overlay"><span class="g-caption">Nuestras Herramientas</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="g-item">
                <div class="g-placeholder"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i><span>Corte + Barba</span></div>
                <div class="g-overlay"><span class="g-caption">Look Completo</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="g-item">
                <div class="g-placeholder"><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i><span>Skin Fade</span></div>
                <div class="g-overlay"><span class="g-caption">Skin Fade</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- NOSOTROS -->
<section class="section-std" id="nosotros">
    <div class="slabel">Quiénes Somos</div>
    <h2 class="stitle">Tu Barbería de Confianza</h2>
    <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-visual">
            <div class="vip-mono">VIP</div>
            <div class="stats-strip">
                <div class="stat-c"><div class="stat-num">6+</div><div class="stat-lbl">Años</div></div>
                <div class="stat-c"><div class="stat-num">2.4K+</div><div class="stat-lbl">Clientes</div></div>
                <div class="stat-c"><div class="stat-num">4.9★</div><div class="stat-lbl">Google</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="hours-table">
                <div class="hour-row"><span class="day">Lunes – Viernes</span><span class="time">9:00 – 20:00</span></div>
                <div class="hour-row"><span class="day">Sábado</span><span class="time">9:00 – 17:00</span></div>
                <div class="hour-row closed"><span class="day">Domingo</span><span class="time">Cerrado</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-text">
            <p>Llevamos más de 6 años siendo el punto de referencia para el caballero granadino que cuida su imagen. Sin prisas, sin improvisación.</p>
            <p>Cada corte es una conversación. Escuchamos lo que buscas, analizamos tu tipo de cabello y ejecutamos con precisión quirúrgica.</p>
            <ul class="features-list">
                <li>Especialistas en degradados y skin fade</li>
                <li>Arreglo y perfilado de barba profesional</li>
                <li>Definición y diseño de cejas para caballero</li>
                <li>Reserva online disponible 24/7</li>
                <li>Sin esperas innecesarias</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- MAPA -->
<div class="map-section">
    <div class="slabel">Cómo Llegar</div>
    <h2 class="stitle" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:0">C. Pintor Zuloaga, 22 · Ronda · Granada</h2>
    <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe
            src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Calle+Pintor+Zuloaga+22+18005+Granada+Spain&t=&z=16&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed"
            allowfullscreen=""
            loading="lazy"
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            title="Ubicación Barbería VIP Granada">
        </iframe>
    </div>
</div>

